<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3548> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3548" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Envoy with Sulla on the first mission to Bocchus (Sall. Iug. 102; App. Num. 4, where, as against Sallust's account, he is given the lead). See 106, Legates." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3525> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3525" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under Marius in Numidia (see above, Envoys, and Promagistrates, on Sulla)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3523> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3523" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Sent by Marius in Numidia to negotiate with Bocchus of Mauretania (Sall. Iug. 100; 102; App. Num. 4; see Promagistrates, on Sulla, and Lieutenants, on Manlius)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3509> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3509" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under Marius in Numidia, and protected the march to Capsa by seizing Lares (Sall. Iug. 86.1; 90.2; cf. App. Num. 4; also Fenestella fr. 12 Peter, in Plin. NH 33.21; and RE s. v. \"Manilius\" no. 3)." .
